data.title: Dave Davies of The Kinks in Norfolk, CT (4/6/2018)
data.meta_description: Dave Davies of The Kinks is performing live at Infinity Music Hall Norfolk, CT on 4/6/2018
data.text:
back to calendar ›

Dave Davies of The Kinks

Share this event:

The Rolling Stones call themselves the greatest R&R band in the world, but admit, if the Kinks were still around, they’d be sharing that title…Infinity Hall Presents - Dave Davies! Original and founding member of the Rock N’ Roll Hall Of Fame group, “The KINKS”. Dave and band will rock you from retro to the present as you’ll hear “You Really Got Me”, “All Of The Day and All Of The Night”, ”Celluloid Hero”, “Come Dancing”, “Destroyer” plus more of the band’s hits and new material as well.

Dave Davies
